                  straightforward. Hence it is not possible to infer
                  the delivered dose directly from the PET
                  distribution. To overcome this problem and enable
                  therapy monitoring, beta(+)-distributions are
                  simulated on the basis of the treatment plan and
                  compared with the measured ones. Following the
